                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Martin</persName>, consul at
                        Nanking, to Mr. <persName type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nanking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-08-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 7, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Sovereign rights of China being guaranteed, Viceroy willing Whangpu conservation
                    be carried out and expects inspector-general of customs to represent China.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Martin.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
